title: LiquidityPoolDepositResult
description:
LiquidityPoolDepositResult is an XDR Union defines as:

```text union LiquidityPoolDepositResult switch (LiquidityPoolDepositResultCode code) { case LIQUIDITY_POOL_DEPOSIT_SUCCESS: void; case LIQUIDITY_POOL_DEPOSIT_MALFORMED: case LIQUIDITY_POOL_DEPOSIT_NO_TRUST: case LIQUIDITY_POOL_DEPOSIT_NOT_AUTHORIZED: case LIQUIDITY_POOL_DEPOSIT_UNDERFUNDED: case LIQUIDITY_POOL_DEPOSIT_LINE_FULL: case LIQUIDITY_POOL_DEPOSIT_BAD_PRICE: case LIQUIDITY_POOL_DEPOSIT_POOL_FULL: void; }; ```
